<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Complejidad Algorítmica – Entrenador de Examen</title>
<style>
  @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=JetBrains+Mono:wght@400;600;700&family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700&display=swap');

  :root {
    --bg: #0d1117;
    --surface: #161b22;
    --surface2: #1c2330;
    --border: #30363d;
    --text: #e6edf3;
    --muted: #7d8590;
    --green: #3fb950;
    --red: #f85149;
    --yellow: #d29922;
    --blue: #58a6ff;
    --purple: #bc8cff;
    --cyan: #79c0ff;
    --orange: #ffa657;
    --easy: #238636;
    --med: #9e6a03;
    --hard: #da3633;
    --vhard: #8957e5;
  }

  * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

  body {
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    background: var(--bg);
    color: var(--text);
    min-height: 100vh;
  }

  /* ── HEADER ── */
  header {
    background: var(--surface);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    padding: 16px 24px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    position: sticky;
    top: 0;
    z-index: 100;
  }
  .logo { font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace; font-size: 1rem; color: var(--blue); }
  .logo span { color: var(--muted); }
  .stats-bar { display: flex; gap: 20px; }
  .stat { text-align: center; }
  .stat-val { font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace; font-size: 1.1rem; font-weight: 700; }
  .stat-lbl { font-size: 0.65rem; color: var(--muted); text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: .05em; }
  .stat-val.green { color: var(--green); }
  .stat-val.yellow { color: var(--yellow); }
  .stat-val.blue { color: var(--blue); }

  /* ── LAYOUT ── */
  .container { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 260px 1fr; min-height: calc(100vh - 57px); }

  /* ── SIDEBAR ── */
  aside {
    background: var(--surface);
    border-right: 1px solid var(--border);
    padding: 16px 0;
    overflow-y: auto;
    max-height: calc(100vh - 57px);
    position: sticky;
    top: 57px;
  }
  .sidebar-title {
    font-size: 0.7rem; font-weight: 600; text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: .08em; color: var(--muted); padding: 8px 16px 6px;
  }
  .sidebar-section { margin-bottom: 8px; }
  .level-badge {
    display: inline-block; font-size: 0.6rem; font-weight: 700;
    text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: .06em;
    padding: 2px 7px; border-radius: 20px; margin-right: 6px;
  }
  .badge-easy { background: #1f3d26; color: var(--green); }
  .badge-med  { background: #3d2f08; color: var(--yellow); }
  .badge-hard { background: #3d1515; color: var(--red); }
  .badge-vhard{ background: #2d1f4a; color: var(--purple); }

  .ex-btn {
    width: 100%; text-align: left; background: none; border: none;
    color: var(--muted); cursor: pointer; padding: 6px 16px;
    font-size: 0.8rem; font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px;
    border-left: 3px solid transparent; transition: all .15s;
  }
  .ex-btn:hover { background: var(--surface2); color: var(--text); }
  .ex-btn.active { background: var(--surface2); color: var(--blue); border-left-color: var(--blue); }
  .ex-btn.done-ok { color: var(--green); }
  .ex-btn.done-ok::after { content: '✓'; margin-left: auto; }
  .ex-btn.done-fail { color: var(--red); }
  .ex-btn.done-fail::after { content: '✗'; margin-left: auto; }
  .ex-btn.revealed { color: var(--yellow); }
  .ex-btn.revealed::after { content: '👁'; margin-left: auto; font-size: .7rem; }

  /* ── MAIN ── */
  main { padding: 32px; overflow-y: auto; }

  .ex-header { margin-bottom: 20px; }
  .ex-meta { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 12px; margin-bottom: 8px; }
  .ex-num { font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace; color: var(--muted); font-size: 0.9rem; }
  .ex-pts { font-size: 0.75rem; background: var(--surface2); color: var(--cyan); padding: 2px 8px; border-radius: 4px; }
  .ex-title { font-size: 1.2rem; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 6px; }
  .ex-desc { color: var(--muted); font-size: 0.85rem; line-height: 1.5; }

  /* ── CODE BLOCK ── */
  .code-block {
    background: var(--surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 8px;
    overflow: visible;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    position: relative;
  }
  .code-lines-wrap {
    border-radius: 0 0 8px 8px;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .code-header {
    background: var(--surface2);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    padding: 8px 16px;
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    color: var(--muted);
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
  }

  .code-line {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    min-height: 36px;
    padding: 4px 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #1c2330;
    transition: background .1s;
  }
  .code-line:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
  .code-line:hover { background: rgba(88,166,255,.03); }
  .code-line.line-correct { background: rgba(63,185,80,.06); }
  .code-line.line-wrong   { background: rgba(248,81,73,.06); }
  .code-line.line-revealed { background: rgba(210,153,34,.06); }

  .line-num {
    width: 36px; min-width: 36px; text-align: right;
    color: var(--muted); padding: 0 10px 0 0; font-size: 0.75rem;
    user-select: none; flex-shrink: 0;
  }
  .line-code {
    flex: 1; min-width: 0; padding: 0 8px;
    white-space: pre; overflow: hidden; text-overflow: ellipsis;
    font-size: 0.83rem;
  }
  .line-answer {
    width: 170px; min-width: 170px; flex-shrink: 0;
    padding: 0 10px;
    display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 6px;
  }
  .line-answer.no-answer { width: 0; min-width: 0; padding: 0; }

  /* ── TOKEN SELECTOR ── */
  .token-selector {
    position: relative;
    display: block;
    width: 100%;
  }
  .token-display {
    background: var(--surface2);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 5px;
    padding: 5px 10px;
    cursor: pointer;
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    color: var(--muted);
    white-space: nowrap;
    transition: border-color .15s, color .15s;
    width: 100%;
    box-sizing: border-box;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    gap: 6px;
  }
  .token-display::after {
    content: '▾';
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    color: var(--muted);
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }
  .token-display.correct::after,
  .token-display.wrong::after,
  .token-display.revealed-ans::after { content: ''; }
  .token-display:hover { border-color: var(--blue); color: var(--text); }
  .token-display.selected { color: var(--cyan); border-color: var(--cyan); background: rgba(121,192,255,.1); }
  .token-display.correct  { color: var(--green); border-color: var(--green); background: rgba(63,185,80,.1); }
  .token-display.wrong    { color: var(--red);   border-color: var(--red);   background: rgba(248,81,73,.1); }
  .token-display.revealed-ans { color: var(--yellow); border-color: var(--yellow); background: rgba(210,153,34,.1); }

  .token-dropdown {
    position: absolute; top: calc(100% + 4px); right: 0; left: auto; z-index: 200;
    background: var(--surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 6px;
    box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(0,0,0,.6);
    min-width: 150px;
    display: none;
    flex-direction: column;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .token-dropdown.open { display: none; } /* modal used instead */
  .token-opt {
    padding: 8px 16px;
    cursor: pointer;
    font-size: 0.82rem;
    color: var(--text);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    transition: background .1s;
    white-space: nowrap;
  }
  .token-opt:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
  .token-opt:hover { background: var(--surface2); color: var(--blue); }

  .line-status { font-size: 0.8rem; }

  /* ── COMPLEXITY EXPLANATION ── */
  .complexity-note {
    font-size: 0.7rem; color: var(--muted); margin-left: 4px;
    font-style: italic;
  }

  /* ── RESULT PANEL ── */
  .result-panel {
    background: var(--surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 16px 20px;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    display: none;
  }
  .result-panel.show { display: block; }
  .result-panel h3 { font-size: 0.9rem; margin-bottom: 10px; }
  .result-row { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; padding: 6px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); font-size: 0.83rem; }
  .result-row:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
  .total-complexity { font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace; font-size: 1.1rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--cyan); }
  .result-correct { color: var(--green); }
  .result-wrong   { color: var(--red); }

  /* ── SOLUTION PANEL ── */
  .solution-panel {
    background: rgba(210,153,34,.05);
    border: 1px solid rgba(210,153,34,.3);
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 16px 20px;
    margin-top: 12px;
    display: none;
  }
  .solution-panel.show { display: block; }
  .solution-panel h3 { color: var(--yellow); font-size: 0.9rem; margin-bottom: 10px; }
  .solution-line { font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace; font-size: 0.82rem; margin-bottom: 4px; }
  .solution-exp  { color: var(--muted); font-size: 0.78rem; margin-left: 16px; margin-bottom: 8px; line-height: 1.4; }

  /* ── BUTTONS ── */
  .btn-row { display: flex; gap: 12px; flex-wrap: wrap; margin-bottom: 16px; }
  .btn {
    padding: 9px 20px;
    border-radius: 6px;
    border: none;
    cursor: pointer;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    transition: opacity .15s, transform .1s;
  }
  .btn:hover { opacity: 0.85; transform: translateY(-1px); }
  .btn:active { transform: translateY(0); }
  .btn-primary { background: var(--blue); color: #000; }
  .btn-secondary { background: var(--surface2); color: var(--text); border: 1px solid var(--border); }
  .btn-danger { background: rgba(248,81,73,.15); color: var(--red); border: 1px solid rgba(248,81,73,.3); }
  .btn-warn { background: rgba(210,153,34,.15); color: var(--yellow); border: 1px solid rgba(210,153,34,.3); }

  /* ── PROGRESS BAR ── */
  .progress-bar { background: var(--surface2); border-radius: 4px; height: 6px; margin-bottom: 24px; }
  .progress-fill { height: 100%; border-radius: 4px; background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--blue), var(--purple)); transition: width .4s ease; }

  /* syntax highlighting */
  .kw  { color: #ff7b72; }
  .fn  { color: #d2a8ff; }
  .num { color: #79c0ff; }
  .op  { color: #79c0ff; }
  .var { color: #e6edf3; }
  .cmt { color: #7d8590; font-style: italic; }

  /* ── TOKEN MODAL (all sizes) ── */
  .token-modal-overlay {
    display: none;
    position: fixed; inset: 0; z-index: 1000;
    background: rgba(0,0,0,.65);
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    padding: 20px;
  }
  .token-modal-overlay.open { display: flex; }
  .token-modal {
    background: var(--surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 12px;
    width: 100%; max-width: 420px;
    padding: 20px 0 16px;
    box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(0,0,0,.7);
  }
  /* On very small screens, slide up from bottom instead */
  @media(max-width: 480px) {
    .token-modal-overlay { align-items: flex-end; padding: 0; }
    .token-modal { border-radius: 16px 16px 0 0; max-width: 100%; padding-bottom: 32px; }
  }
  .token-modal-title {
    font-size: 0.72rem; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: .07em;
    color: var(--muted); text-align: center; padding: 0 20px 12px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); margin-bottom: 8px;
  }
  .token-modal-code {
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace; font-size: 0.78rem;
    color: var(--cyan); text-align: center; padding: 6px 20px 10px;
    white-space: pre-wrap; word-break: break-all;
  }
  .token-modal-opts {
    display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 8px; padding: 4px 16px;
  }
  .token-modal-opt {
    background: var(--surface2);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 12px 8px;
    text-align: center;
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 0.88rem;
    color: var(--text);
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: background .1s, border-color .1s;
    -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;
  }
  .token-modal-opt:active { background: rgba(88,166,255,.15); border-color: var(--blue); }
  .token-modal-cancel {
    margin: 12px 16px 0;
    width: calc(100% - 32px);
    padding: 12px;
    background: none;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 8px;
    color: var(--muted);
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    cursor: pointer;
    text-align: center;
  }

  /* responsive */
  @media(max-width: 700px) {
    .container { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    aside { position: relative; max-height: 180px; top: 0; overflow-y: auto; }
    main { padding: 12px; }
    .stats-bar { gap: 10px; }

    /* Code lines: stack vertically on mobile */
    .code-line {
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: flex-start;
      min-height: unset;
      padding: 8px 0;
      gap: 6px;
    }
    .code-line .line-num {
      display: none; /* save space */
    }
    .line-code {
      padding: 0 12px;
      font-size: 0.78rem;
      white-space: pre-wrap;
      word-break: break-all;
      width: 100%;
    }
    .line-answer {
      min-width: unset;
      width: calc(100% - 24px);
      margin: 0 12px;
      padding: 0;
    }
    .token-display {
      width: 100%;
      padding: 8px 12px;
      font-size: 0.85rem;
      text-align: left;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
    }
    .code-header { flex-direction: column; gap: 4px; }
    .ex-title { font-size: 1rem; }
    .btn { padding: 10px 16px; font-size: 0.82rem; }
  }

  /* welcome */
  .welcome {
    display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    height: 60vh; text-align: center; gap: 16px;
  }
  .welcome h2 { font-size: 1.6rem; color: var(--blue); }
  .welcome p  { color: var(--muted); max-width: 460px; line-height: 1.6; }
  .welcome-grid {
    display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(2,1fr); gap: 12px; margin-top: 8px; width: 320px;
  }
  .wcard {
    background: var(--surface); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 12px; text-align: center;
  }
  .wcard .n { font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace; font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: 700; }
  .wcard .l { font-size: 0.7rem; color: var(--muted); text-transform: uppercase; }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- Mobile token picker modal -->
<div class="token-modal-overlay" id="token-modal-overlay" onclick="handleModalOverlayClick(event)">
  <div class="token-modal" id="token-modal">
    <div class="token-modal-title" id="token-modal-title">Selecciona la complejidad</div>
    <div class="token-modal-code" id="token-modal-code"></div>
    <div class="token-modal-opts" id="token-modal-opts"></div>
    <button class="token-modal-cancel" onclick="closeTokenModal()">Cancelar</button>
  </div>
</div>

<header>
  <div class="logo">O<span>(</span>n<span>)</span>&nbsp;Trainer&nbsp;<span style="color:var(--muted);font-size:.8rem">— Algoritmia y Complejidad</span></div>
  <div class="stats-bar">
    <div class="stat"><div class="stat-val green" id="st-ok">0</div><div class="stat-lbl">Correctos</div></div>
    <div class="stat"><div class="stat-val yellow" id="st-total">0</div><div class="stat-lbl">Resueltos</div></div>
    <div class="stat"><div class="stat-val blue" id="st-pct">0%</div><div class="stat-lbl">Precisión</div></div>
  </div>
</header>

<div class="container">
  <aside id="sidebar"></aside>
  <main id="main-content">
    <div class="welcome" id="welcome">
      <div style="font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:2.5rem;color:var(--blue)">T(n)</div>
      <h2>Entrenador de Complejidad Algorítmica</h2>
      <p>60 ejercicios progresivos para dominar el análisis de complejidad antes de tu examen. Analiza cada línea, selecciona la notación correcta y obtén la complejidad total.</p>
      <div class="welcome-grid">
        <div class="wcard"><div class="n" style="color:var(--green)">5</div><div class="l">Muy fáciles</div></div>
        <div class="wcard"><div class="n" style="color:var(--yellow)">15</div><div class="l">Intermedios</div></div>
        <div class="wcard"><div class="n" style="color:var(--red)">20</div><div class="l">Difíciles</div></div>
        <div class="wcard"><div class="n" style="color:var(--purple)">20</div><div class="l">Muy difíciles</div></div>
      </div>
      <p style="font-size:.8rem;color:var(--muted)">Selecciona un ejercicio en el panel izquierdo para empezar.</p>
    </div>
    <div id="exercise-view" style="display:none"></div>
  </main>
</div>

<script>
// ─────────────────────────────────────────
// TOKENS disponibles
// ─────────────────────────────────────────
const TOKENS = ['O(1)','O(log n)','O(n)','O(n log n)','O(n²)','O(n² log n)','O(n³)','O(2^n)','O(n!)'];

// ─────────────────────────────────────────
// EJERCICIOS  (60 en total)
// Cada línea: { code: string, complexity: string|null (null = no responder), note: string }
// answer: complejidad total del algoritmo
// ─────────────────────────────────────────
const EXERCISES = [
// ══════════════ MUY FÁCILES (1-5) ══════════════
{
  id:1, level:'easy', pts:0.5,
  title:'Suma de un número',
  desc:'Un bucle simple que recorre n elementos una sola vez.',
  lines:[
    {code:'for (i = 1; i <= n; i++)',  cx:'O(n)',   note:'Itera n veces'},
    {code:'    sum++;',                  cx:'O(1)',   note:'Operación constante'},
  ],
  answer:'O(n)',
  explanation:'El bucle externo ejecuta n iteraciones. Dentro solo hay una operación O(1). Total: O(n) × O(1) = O(n).'
},
{
  id:2, level:'easy', pts:0.5,
  title:'Asignación simple',
  desc:'Tres instrucciones secuenciales sin bucles.',
  lines:[
    {code:'x = 5;',     cx:'O(1)', note:'Asignación constante'},
    {code:'y = x + 3;', cx:'O(1)', note:'Operación aritmética'},
    {code:'z = y * 2;', cx:'O(1)', note:'Operación aritmética'},
  ],
  answer:'O(1)',
  explanation:'Tres operaciones O(1) en secuencia. T(n) = O(1)+O(1)+O(1) = O(1). No depende de ninguna variable de entrada.'
},
{
  id:3, level:'easy', pts:0.5,
  title:'Bucle hasta n/2',
  desc:'Un bucle que va hasta la mitad de n.',
  lines:[
    {code:'for (i = 1; i <= n/2; i++)', cx:'O(n)', note:'n/2 iteraciones → O(n)'},
    {code:'    x = x + i;',              cx:'O(1)', note:'Suma constante'},
  ],
  answer:'O(n)',
  explanation:'Aunque el bucle solo hace n/2 iteraciones, en notación asintótica las constantes se eliminan: O(n/2) = O(n).'
},
{
  id:4, level:'easy', pts:0.5,
  title:'Condicional simple',
  desc:'Un if-else dentro de un bucle.',
  lines:[
    {code:'for (i = 0; i < n; i++) {', cx:'O(n)', note:'n iteraciones'},
    {code:'    if (a[i] > 0)',          cx:'O(1)', note:'Comparación'},
    {code:'        sum += a[i];',       cx:'O(1)', note:'Suma'},
    {code:'    else',                   cx:null,   note:null},
    {code:'        sum -= a[i];',       cx:'O(1)', note:'Resta'},
    {code:'}',                          cx:null,   note:null},
  ],
  answer:'O(n)',
  explanation:'El bucle hace n iteraciones. Las operaciones dentro son O(1). El if-else no añade más complejidad. Total: O(n).'
},
{
  id:5, level:'easy', pts:0.5,
  title:'Dos bucles secuenciales',
  desc:'Dos bucles independientes uno tras otro.',
  lines:[
    {code:'for (i = 0; i < n; i++)',   cx:'O(n)', note:'Primer bucle'},
    {code:'    a[i] = i;',              cx:'O(1)', note:'Asignación'},
    {code:'for (j = 0; j < n; j++)',   cx:'O(n)', note:'Segundo bucle'},
    {code:'    b[j] = j*2;',            cx:'O(1)', note:'Asignación'},
  ],
  answer:'O(n)',
  explanation:'T(n) = O(n) + O(n) = O(2n) = O(n). Dos bucles secuenciales de n iteraciones. Las constantes se eliminan.'
},

// ══════════════ INTERMEDIOS (6-20) ══════════════
{
  id:6, level:'med', pts:1,
  title:'Bucle with while de mitades',
  desc:'For externo + while que divide j entre 2 en cada iteración.',
  lines:[
    {code:'for (i = 1; i <= n; i++) {',  cx:'O(n)',     note:'n iteraciones externas'},
    {code:'    j = n;',                   cx:'O(1)',     note:'Asignación'},
    {code:'    while (j > 0) {',          cx:'O(log n)', note:'j se divide entre 2 → log₂n veces'},
    {code:'        sum++;',               cx:'O(1)',     note:'Operación constante'},
